#

Pineapple Teriyaki Burger

25 min
$12
480 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

Quick MealFamily-FriendlyBBQSummer

Description

A juicy burger topped with sweet and tangy teriyaki sauce and grilled pineapple, perfect for a quick and delicious meal.

Ingredients

  • ground beef (or turkey): 1 lb
  • teriyaki sauce: 1/2 cup
  • pineapple slices: 4 slices
  • burger buns: 4
  • lettuce leaves: 4
  • sliced tomatoes: 1
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
